---
kind: rule
version: "1.0"
name: deno-cache
description: "Directs agents to the correct Deno module cache location within the pixi environment."
activation: always
---
## Deno Module Cache Location

The Deno module cache is located inside the pixi environment, **not** in the user's home directory:

```
./.pixi/envs/default/var/cache/deno
```

When looking for cached Deno module source code, inspect this path rather than `~/.cache/deno`.
